name: CheckSwing
tag_list: social-network, baseball, sports, recruitment, parents, coaches, players, blog, video
overview:
CheckSwing is a baseball social network that connects baseball people from all levels.

CheckSwing was launched to bring together baseball players, coaches, parents and scouts to connect, share ideas, mentor and improve their baseball skills and knowledge. Members write blogs, have discussions, upload video and photos and create groups for their team or league.

CheckSwing Groups include a Recruit Me group, which is a free recruitment source for high school and college players, an MLB Alumni and Minor League Alumni Group, a Youth Baseball Coaches Group, a Baseball Moms group, a College Players Looking to Play Pro group, as well as groups for hundreds of teams and leagues worldwide.
